cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a video analytics system that uses deep neural networks for object detection on edge devices. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also introduces dynamic approximation techniques to achieve desired inference latency and accuracy trade-off, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Finally, the paper discusses the comparison of their approach with other deep neural network models, which falls under neural networks (cs.NE) category.
